flowchart TD
    Response[Prediction Response] --> SaveHistory[insert_query_history<br/>Save to SQLite]
    SaveHistory --> HistoryDb[(SQLite query_history)]

    HistoryDb --> HistoryApi[GET /history<br/>History & Stats]
    HistoryDb --> VerifyApi[POST /history/{entry_id}/verify<br/>Store Verified Label]
    VerifyApi --> Verified[verified_label + verified_at]

    Response --> AutoCheck[maybe_auto_retrain<br/>Periodic Check]
    AutoCheck --> RetrainFlow[run_verified_retraining]
    Verified --> RetrainFlow
    ManualRetrain[POST /retrain] --> RetrainFlow
    StatusApi[GET /training/stats<br/>Retraining Status] --> HistoryDb

    RetrainFlow --> VerifiedData[get_verified_training_data]
    VerifiedData --> Bundle[build_retraining_bundle<br/>Combine Base + Verified]
    Bundle --> Train[train_model<br/>Retrain on Combined Data]
    Train --> SaveModel[save model + metrics<br/>replace_model]
    SaveModel --> Feedback[Feedback Loop<br/>Improved Model]